{"tid":158501,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"李城歐聯冠軍有28倍","createTime":"2017-03-16T10:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T17:23:21.000Z","uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eeadbdfb1e1f726d2198e99a538b44ea5477a455","tid":158501,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T10:18:01.000Z","msg":"歐聯8強全部出爐，結果西甲球隊成為大贏家，巴塞隆拿、皇家馬德里同馬德里體育會全部過關，而且巴塞同拜仁慕尼黑被歐洲博彩公司捧成4.75倍冠軍大熱，馬會足智彩就列巴塞為3.4倍為頂頭大熱，拜仁3.5倍居次，衞冕嘅皇家馬德里就係4.7倍第三熱門。至於英超唯一代表兼8強新丁李斯特城有28倍，屬8強最大冷門。8強抽籤將喺香港時間周五晚7點舉行，到時就知邊隊抽好籤。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歐聯8強冠軍賠率&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n球隊(聯賽)　　　　　賠率&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n巴塞隆拿(西甲)　　　3.4倍&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n拜仁慕尼黑(德甲)　　3.5倍&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n皇家馬德里(西甲)　　4.7倍&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n馬德里體育會(西甲)　8倍&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n多蒙特(德甲)　　　　8.5倍&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n祖雲達斯(意甲)　　　10倍&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n摩納哥(法甲)　　　　20倍&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n李斯特城(英超)　　　28倍&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬會足智彩賠率，截至3月16日下午2時<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上樓啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58ab4073a4bcaf51a2904011f66954bd92b7a9de","tid":158501,"uid":1289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T10:19:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c28f04ab378100f89dbbf6af19ebeed995a0e7b","tid":158501,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T10:19:10.000Z","msg":"28咁少，點上"},{"pid":"df17f51ac71f74c9bc00dba20fb04b241ddabd4e","tid":158501,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T10:19:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>28咁少，點上</blockquote><br />\n買得大賠得大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d358f2b998fe91549d0bedffdfb4d0da35e9293","tid":158501,"uid":23160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T10:22:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>28咁少，點上</blockquote><br />\n買得大賠得大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大大下就冇28<img src=\"/assets/fac